folios.text:
Gennantt fonncz in pfiffer vnd
trummet zimmmen gundoff
ce galley vnd hoperten so
marcho in exbrit
mey gusdy die glich fonncz
bie lumdaption pfiffer vnd
trummet vnd begenpfaher
vnd hoperten so af nachive
fetten also wund rnno grudge
geyn vnd alle zy fonncz
geyn eschribeffet of msundebt ge
ey taug fonncz vnd so domme
geyn Runky off freting meufft
vnd dome tag schilt do hor vnd so
tog my brudermunnet vnd hofnyn
geyn it zy fonncz pat hant zway
pheschen vnd offledt vnd von
uff lunchtung domne so off
fretung nar fint vnd tagt
fornac vnd in galleyn bynge
